#exportGroup
	h4 3. Export
	.btn.btn-success.btn-block#shareButton
		span.fa.fa-share
		| &nbsp;&nbsp;Share your work
	.btn.btn-success.btn-block#downloadButton
		span.fa.fa-download
		| &nbsp;&nbsp;Download

	.modal.fade#downloadModal
		.modal-dialog
			.modal-content
				.modal-header
					button.bootbox-close-button.close(data-dismiss="modal") Ã—
					h4.modal-title Download
				.modal-body
					h4 Download stl for 3d printer
					p
						| Select the stud size that works best for your 3d printer.
						| If you don't know the size, download and print the&nbsp;
						a(href="/download/testStrip.zip") test strip
						| .
					center
						img(src="/img/testStrip.png" width=300)
					p
						| To connect LEGO studs into the test strip, this size works best:
						select.form-control#studSizeSelect
							option -3
							option -2
							option -1
							option(selected="selected") 0
							option +1
							option +2
							option +3
					p
						| To connect test strip studs into LEGO bricks, this size works best:
						select.form-control#holeSizeSelect
							option -3
							option -2
							option -1
							option(selected="selected") 0
							option +1
							option +2
							option +3
					br
					.btn.btn-success.btn-block#stlDownloadButton
						span.fa.fa-download
						| &nbsp;&nbsp;Download stl for 3D printer

					h4 Download Instructions
					.btn.btn-success.btn-block#downloadPdfButton
						span.fa.fa-download
						| &nbsp;&nbsp;Download pdf LEGO instructions
				.modal-footer
					button.btn.btn-primary(data-dismiss="modal") Close
